# ============================================================================
# NOTES FOR CONTRIBUTORS
# ============================================================================
#
# 1. CODEOWNERS rules are evaluated bottom-up (more specific rules override general ones)
# 2. All paths are relative to repository root
# 3. At least one code owner approval is required for PRs
# 4. Code owners are automatically requested for review when their code is modified
# 5. You can use teams (@org/team-name) or individuals (@username)
#
# For more information:
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
